title: PBE Clash isn't working

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: My friends and I were waiting to test out clash on the PBE. Then all of a sudden it ended and their is no news about it anywhere. Just wondering what happened.

replies.body: It's likely that it had already ended since I believe Clash is still only being tested in certain regions that might be ahead of the NA time zones.
